 	<div id="main-article-info">

		
		
			<h1 itemprop="name headline  "
								>David Simon: 'There are now  two Americas. My country is a horror show'</h1>
		
					<div itemprop="description" id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"                        	        data-component="Article:standfirst_cta"			>The creator of The Wire, David Simon, delivered an impromptu speech about the divide between rich and poor in America at the <a href="http://fodi.sydneyoperahouse.com/some-people-are-more-equal-than-others">Festival of Dangerous Ideas</a> in Sydney, and how capitalism has lost sight of its social compact. This is an edited extract</div>
		
		
  	</div>

